{"tid":1492122,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"輿論戰好重要！文宣文宣文宣！","createTime":"2019-08-20T16:37:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-20T19:50:14.000Z","uid":912,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"c5c898c70ab93b57b726e6a39f4273b1ae6c6c7c","tid":1492122,"uid":912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T16:37:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/KvGAVEKQDQg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FKvGAVEKQDQg&d=DXuv2gayA%2Byyjyt3RGK41J1DrXAeA17tgS6Eh9jzous%3D&h=ca8e05e6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/KvGAVEKQDQg</a><br />\n<br />\n台灣果邊明居正嘅分析<br />\n<br />\n文宣真係好重要！<br />\n要爭取中間遊離分子嘅支持！<br />\n繼續不割蓆！不分化！<br />\n9月後大家真係要考慮罷課<br />\n如果學佢咁講 1-5 返工返學 週末上街<br />\n會好易淡化<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家要加油！長期抗爭爭取民主自由<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f10e2519ba056d82c6fc74c637b6ea6f9946a21","tid":1492122,"uid":2562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T16:39:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PXcMrux.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPXcMrux.jpg&h=54112853&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PN4V4gd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPN4V4gd.jpg&h=bf41982c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/20/233941_35db8952adc66a9b8fad2b475503a348.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F20%2F233941_35db8952adc66a9b8fad2b475503a348.jpeg&h=ba2d15e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0y2D12U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0y2D12U.jpg&h=c7bab806&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"